name: SoloMemo
description:
SoloMemo
Drop by to celebrate my first 100 followers on TT! Because we can be lonely, but never alone! Alone we are nobody!
Thank you Universe!
Thanks to all of you who support me!

Art Description: SoloMemo is a totally intuitive soundtrack. It is about that solitude that plagues us in pandemic times and that makes us want to be close to our own! All instruments were recorded by music producer @originallerry!
Video taken on the outskirts of the city of Feira de Santana, Bahia, Brazil!
